{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-awesome-readme-js","path":"/agamm/awesome-developer-first/readme/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Track Awesome List"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"84e7bd06-6cca-5ff8-9d9c-4111b1d576f3","html":"<h1 id=\"awesome-developer-first-awesome\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#awesome-developer-first-awesome\" aria-label=\"awesome developer first awesome permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Awesome Developer-First <a href=\"https://awesome.re\"><img src=\"https://awesome.re/badge.svg\" alt=\"Awesome\"></a></h1>\n<p>A curated list of awesome developer-first tools, products and resources.</p>\n<p>The definition of developer-first for this repo is:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Developers are the target audience.</li>\n<li>\"Headless\", \"API-first\", \"SaaS\" are frequently used keywords.</li>\n<li>Usually, this means that the front page has some code examples.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"diff\"><pre class=\"language-diff\"><code class=\"language-diff\"><span class=\"token inserted-sign inserted\"><span class=\"token prefix inserted\">+</span> 👀 Watch this repo to get notifications about new products we find</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"contents\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#contents\" aria-label=\"contents permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Contents</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#analytics\">Analytics</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#authentication--identity\">Authentication &#x26; Identity</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#cicd\">CI/CD</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#cms-headless\">CMS (headless)</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#code-quality\">Code Quality</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#computer-vision\">Computer Vision</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#databases--spreadsheets\">Databases &#x26; Spreadsheets</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#deployment-hosting\">Deployment Hosting</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#discussions\">Discussions</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#documentation\">Documentation</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#environment--secret-management\">Environment &#x26; Secret Management</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#geo\">GEO</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#ide\">IDE</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#localization\">Localization</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#mail\">Mail</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#media\">Media</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#messaging\">Messaging</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#misc\">Misc</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#monitoring\">Monitoring</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#natural-language-processing\">Natural Language Processing</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#payments\">Payments</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#repo\">Repo</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#scraping\">Scraping</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#search\">Search</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#shipping\">Shipping</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#testing\">Testing</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"analytics\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#analytics\" aria-label=\"analytics permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Analytics</h2>\n<p><em>Track web/app visitors.</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://mixpanel.com/\">Mixpanel</a> - Product analytics and dashboards.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://baremetrics.com/\">Baremetrics</a> - Subscription analytics for Stripe.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://segment.com/\">Segment</a> - Collect user data and send it to your other tools.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://heap.io/\">Heap</a> - Product analytics API for web and mobile, captures all events.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"authentication--identity\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#authentication--identity\" aria-label=\"authentication  identity permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Authentication &#x26; Identity</h2>\n<p><em>Products that handle authentication and user identity for you.</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://auth0.com/\">Auth0</a> - Authentication &#x26; authorization as a service.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://aws.amazon.com/cognito/\">AWS cognito</a> - AWS's authentication as a service.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://developer.okta.com/\">Okta</a> - Embeddable authentication with SSO.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.loginradius.com/\">LoginRadius</a> - Managed user authentication service with SSO.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://firebase.google.com/products/auth\">Firebase Auth</a> - Google Firebase's take on authentication.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://magic.link\">Magic.link</a> - Passwordless (email-based) log in as a service.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"cicd\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#cicd\" aria-label=\"cicd permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>CI/CD</h2>\n<p><em>Continious Integration/Delivery.</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://circleci.com/\">CircleCI</a> - YML to configure your builds, parallel jobs, jobs marketplace.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://gitlab.com/\">Gitlab</a> - Open source CI and hosted solution with Github-like abilities.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"cms-headless\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#cms-headless\" aria-label=\"cms headless permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>CMS (headless)</h2>\n<p><em>Backend only Content Management System, you decide on frontend and consume content via API.</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://contentful.com/\">Contentful</a> - CMS as an API.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://tipe.io/\">Tipe</a> - Open source headless CMS.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.elegantcms.io/\">ElegantCMS</a> - Headless CMS builder.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://ghost.org/\">Ghost</a> - Blog platform, can be used as headless CMS (ex. <a href=\"https://ghost.org/docs/api/v3/hexo/\">with Hexo</a>).</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"code-quality\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#code-quality\" aria-label=\"code quality permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Code Quality</h2>\n<p><em>Check your code quality.</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.sonarsource.com/\">sonarsource</a> - Lint and code quality checks.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.codacy.com/\">Codacy</a> - Automatic code quality checks.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"computer-vision\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#computer-vision\" aria-label=\"computer vision permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Computer Vision</h2>\n<p><em>Manipulate and detect visual data.</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.clarifai.com/\">clarifai</a> - Set of computer vision APIs.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://cloudsight.ai/\">CloudSight</a> - Digital media brand recognition.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/vision\">Google Vision AI</a> - Google's AI vision APIs.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"databases--spreadsheets\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#databases--spreadsheets\" aria-label=\"databases  spreadsheets permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Databases &#x26; Spreadsheets</h2>\n<p><em>Storing data and processing it.</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://airtable.com/\">Airtable</a> - Database and spreadsheet hybrid with an API.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"deployment-hosting\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#deployment-hosting\" aria-label=\"deployment hosting permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Deployment Hosting</h2>\n<p><em>Products that help you deploy your app/website.</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://render.com/\">Render</a> - Deploy from git to a CDN with SSL.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://vercel.com/\">Vercel</a> - Deploy JAMStack (mainly Next.js) via CLI.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.netlify.com/\">Netlify</a> - Deploy JAMStack (mainly Gatsby) via CLI.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.heroku.com/\">Heroku</a> - Deploy via CLI to scalable servers.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.digitalocean.com/products/app-platform/\">Digital Ocean App Platform</a> - Deploy and don't care about infrastructure, works with all major frameworks.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://platform.sh/\">Platform.sh</a> - Continuously deploy full-stack apps.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"discussions\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#discussions\" aria-label=\"discussions permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Discussions</h2>\n<p><em>Comments and forums.</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://commento.io/\">Commento</a> - Privacy centric embeddable comment system.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://muut.io/\">MuutIo</a> - Tools to create a community-driven app.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.turntonetworks.com/\">TurnTo</a> - Ratings, community Q&#x26;A, reviews, and comments as a service.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.bazaarvoice.com/ratings-and-reviews/\">Bazaarvoice</a> - Ratings, reviews as a service.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.yotpo.com/platform/reviews/\">Yotpo</a> - Reviews ratings and Q&#x26;A as a service.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://gitter.im\">Gitter</a> - Chat and networking platform for developers.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"documentation\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#documentation\" aria-label=\"documentation permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Documentation</h2>\n<p><em>Documentation solutions.</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://readme.com/\">readme</a> - Personalized and dynamic developer docs.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://developerhub.io/\">DeveloperHub</a> - Collaborative developer documentation platform.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"environment--secret-management\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#environment--secret-management\" aria-label=\"environment  secret management permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Environment &#x26; Secret Management</h2>\n<p><em>Manage environment variables and secrets for multiple apps or projects.</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.vaultproject.io/\">Vault</a> - API driven secret key management.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://doppler.com/\">Doppler</a> - Environment variable management across projects, in one place.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://1password.com/secrets/\">1Password Secrets Automation</a> - Secrets management with integration to 1Password.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.envkey.com/\">Envkey</a> - Environment management with syncing mechanism for all apps.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"geo\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#geo\" aria-label=\"geo permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>GEO</h2>\n<p><em>Location services.</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://radar.io/\">Radar</a> - Geofencing and geo APIs.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.mapbox.com/\">mapbox</a> - Maps and locations products for devs.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.smartystreets.com/\">SmartyStreets</a> - US Reverse Geocoding and Address Verification APIs.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"ide\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#ide\" aria-label=\"ide permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>IDE</h2>\n<p><em>Products that extend your IDE and help development.</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.codota.com/\">Codota</a> - AI code completions for your IDE.\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.tabnine.com/\">TabNine</a> - Deep learning completion (part of codota).</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.kite.com/\">Kite</a> - AI assistant in your IDE (Python or JS).</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"localization\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#localization\" aria-label=\"localization permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Localization</h2>\n<p><em>Translating your product (also denoted i18n).</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://localazy.com/\">Localazy</a> - App translation built for developers.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"mail\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#mail\" aria-label=\"mail permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Mail</h2>\n<p><em>Sending emails as a service.</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.mailgun.com/\">Mailgun</a> - Send, track, and receive emails.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://sendgrid.com/\">Sendgrid</a> - Email API.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.lob.com/\">Lob</a> - Email and address verification.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://formspree.io/\">FormSpree</a> - Receive form submissions by email.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://hunter.io/\">Hunter.io</a> - Email lead and validation APIs.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://anymailfinder.com\">Anymail finder</a> - Verify and find email APIs.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"media\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#media\" aria-label=\"media permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Media</h2>\n<p><em>Media APIs (optimization, CDN).</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://cloudinary.com/\">Cloudinary</a> - Optimize, create, manage, and deliver images and videos.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.imgix.com/\">imgix</a> - Transforms, optimizes, and cache images.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://imagekit.io/\">ImageKit</a> - Automate image optimization, transformation, and delivery.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://mux.com/\">Mux</a> - APIs to upload, manage, and stream video.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"messaging\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#messaging\" aria-label=\"messaging permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Messaging</h2>\n<p><em>Messaging APIs - SMS, notifications, chats, and VoIP.</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.twilio.com/\">Twilio</a> - SMS, push notifications, and VoIP APIs.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.vonage.com\">Vonage</a> - Video, SMS, chat, and voice APIs.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://getstream.io/\">stream</a> - Feed and chat as a service.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.applozic.com/\">Applozic</a> - Chat SDKs, real-time messaging.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"misc\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#misc\" aria-label=\"misc permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Misc</h2>\n<p><em>Different products that probably don't have a category.</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.actyx.com/\">Actyx</a> - Developer-first factory building.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"monitoring\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#monitoring\" aria-label=\"monitoring permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Monitoring</h2>\n<p><em>Monitoring your production application.</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://sentry.io/\">Sentry</a> - Application monitoring for bugs and performance.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://keen.io/\">KeenIO</a> - Event streaming platform.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://rollbar.com/\">Rollbar</a> - Reports errors in production.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://logrocket.com/\">LogRocket</a> - Replay bugs users had.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"natural-language-processing\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#natural-language-processing\" aria-label=\"natural language processing permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Natural Language Processing</h2>\n<p><em>Interactions with natural language.</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wit.ai\">Wit.ai</a> - Voice/text chatbot framework by Facebook.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://cloud.google.com/dialogflow\">DialogFlow</a> - Voice/text chatbot framework by Google.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"payments\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#payments\" aria-label=\"payments permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Payments</h2>\n<p><em>Handling payments, credit card processing, and invoices.</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://stripe.com/payments\">Stripe Payments</a> - Accept payments and move money globally with APIs.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.braintreepayments.com/\">Braintree</a> - Paypal's take on API-first payments.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://plaid.com/\">Plaid</a> - Accept, send ACH (bank transfers) and get bank information.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://paddle.com/\">Paddle</a> - Revenue delivery platform for SaaS with broad geographical support (unlike stripe at the moment).</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"repo\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#repo\" aria-label=\"repo permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Repo</h2>\n<p><em>Repository and artifacts management.</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://jfrog.com/artifactory/\">Artifactory</a> - Create your own package repository.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://cloudsmith.com/\">cloudsmith</a> - Cloud-native private package management.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"scraping\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#scraping\" aria-label=\"scraping permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Scraping</h2>\n<p><em>Fetching data from websites not via an intended API.</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://apify.com/\">Apify</a> - Turn websites to an API.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://proxycrawl.com/\">proxycrawl</a> - Scrape hard-to-scrape websites with proxies.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.scrapingbee.com/\">ScrapingBee</a> - Using headless browsers and proxies to scrape without being blocked.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://scrapingant.com/\">ScrapingANT</a> - Scrape with headless chrome.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"search\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#search\" aria-label=\"search permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Search</h2>\n<p><em>Index and search your content as a service API.</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.algolia.com/\">Algolia</a> - Search as a service and full suite of search APIs.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://swiftype.com/\">Swiftype</a> - Search as a service (crawlers and React ready).</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.websolr.com/\">Websolr</a> - Open-source and hosted search with Solr.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"shipping\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#shipping\" aria-label=\"shipping permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Shipping</h2>\n<p><em>Creating and handling the shipment of goods.</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.easypost.com/\">easypost</a> - Shipping APIs for e-commerce.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"testing\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#testing\" aria-label=\"testing permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Testing</h2>\n<p><em>Testing tools.</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.testim.io/\">Testim</a> - Frontend testing.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://applitools.com/\">Applitools</a> - Automated visual testing.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://percy.io/\">Percy</a> - Continuous visual testing.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://blackfire.io/\">Blackfire.io</a> - Performance testing.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.chromatic.com/\">Chromatic</a> - Visual UI testing for storybook.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://beeceptor.com/\">Beeceptor</a> - REST API mocking.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"contributing\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#contributing\" a